public class DlaProcessContext

Description: I am class representing the runtime information collected in DLA business process. I hold the instance of the DlApplication business object. I am used by both the activities in DL business process and the JSF components for binding. File: DlaProcessContext.java Module: gov.ca.dmv.ease.app.context.dl Created: Jul 25, 2009
